$ Android SDK: tools/android

At least the → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/cmd_exe/batch-files version (`android.bat`) contains the following message:
"
The "android" command is deprecated.

For manual → development/Android/SDK[SDK], → development/Android/AVD, and project management, please use → development/Android/Studio

For command-line tools, use → development/Android/SDK/dirs/tools/bin/sdkmanager[tools\bin\sdkmanager.bat] and → development/Android/SDK/dirs/tools/bin/avdmanager[tools\bin\avdmanager.bat]
"

